@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Our Commitment to You";
}

<div class="container py-5">
    <header class="text-center mb-5">
        <h1 class="display-4 font-weight-bold text-primary">The SkyDrop Difference</h1>
        <p class="lead text-muted">More than just water, it's a commitment to purity, people, and the planet.</p>
        <hr class="my-4 w-50 mx-auto">
    </header>

    <div class="row align-items-center mb-5 p-4 rounded shadow-sm bg-light">
        <div class="col-md-6 order-md-1">
            <h2 class="text-info mb-3">1. Unwavering Purity & Quality 💧</h2>
            <p class="text-justify">
                At SkyDrop Hydro, purity isn't a goal—it's our standard. Our water undergoes a **rigorous, 7-stage filtration process**, including reverse osmosis and ozone sterilization, to remove every trace of contaminants. We ensure our water isn't just clean; it's **crisp, healthy, and perfectly balanced** for superior taste.
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Certified by the National Water Quality Association (NWQA).</li>
                <li>Daily testing exceeding all federal and state requirements.</li>
                <li>Mineral content optimized for a refreshing drinking experience.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 order-md-2 text-center">
            <img src="~/images/purity-lab.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded shadow-lg" alt="Water Purity Lab" style="max-height: 350px; object-fit: cover;">
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row align-items-center mb-5 p-4 rounded shadow-sm bg-white">
        <div class="col-md-6 order-md-2">
            <h2 class="text-success mb-3">2. Commitment to Sustainability 🌍</h2>
            <p class="text-justify">
                We believe in protecting the source of our future. SkyDrop Hydro is committed to minimizing our environmental footprint through **sustainable sourcing and innovative packaging**. We prioritize the use of **reusable jugs and recycled plastics** across our entire product line.
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>100% recyclable bottles and fully sanitized reusable 5-gallon jugs.</li>
                <li>Local sourcing to reduce transportation emissions.</li>
                <li>Investing 5% of profits into local watershed conservation efforts.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 order-md-1 text-center">
            <img src="~/images/sustainability-jug.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded shadow-lg" alt="Reusable Water Jug" style="max-height: 350px; object-fit: cover;">
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row align-items-center mb-5 p-4 rounded shadow-sm bg-light">
        <div class="col-md-6 order-md-1">
            <h2 class="text-warning mb-3">3. Exceptional & Local Service 🛠️</h2>
            <p class="text-justify">
                When you choose SkyDrop, you're choosing a **local team dedicated to your satisfaction**. From our friendly, reliable delivery drivers to our expert water system technicians, we are here to ensure your experience is hassle-free and refreshing.
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Flexible delivery schedules with easy online management.</li>
                <li>Dedicated local customer support—no automated phone trees!</li>
                <li>Complimentary installation and maintenance checks for all water systems.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 order-md-2 text-center">
            <img src="~/images/friendly-service.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded shadow-lg" alt="Friendly Delivery Driver" style="max-height: 350px; object-fit: cover;">
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center pt-4">
        <h3 class="mb-3 text-secondary">Ready to taste the SkyDrop difference?</h3>
        <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Products" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg pulse-btn">
            View Our Products & Start Hydrating Today! <i class="fas fa-arrow-right ml-2"></i>
        </a>
    </div>

</div>